com.example.parkinggarage.model.users

Class UserBag

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.parkinggarage.model.users.UserBag
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class UserBag
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    A UserBag contains a map of username Strings to Users. The map is a HashMap allowing for quick searching of usernames and a swift sign in process.
